headline: MetLife to Present New Frontier Strategy at December 12 Investor Day
summary: NEW YORK, December 05, 2024--MetLife, Inc. (NYSE: MET) will hold an Investor Day in New York City on Thursday, December 12, 2024, at 8:30 a.m. (ET), where members of MetLife's executive leadership team and other senior leaders will present the company’s New Frontier strategy.
